<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Navigator+ | Road Safety for Singapore's Youth</title>
    <%- include('partials/styles.ejs') %>
    <style>
        body { padding-top: 86px; }

        .hero-emoji-row { font-size: 42px; margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: 14px; }

        .page-hero { padding: 70px 0; }

        /* stat strip now uses global .stat-strip / .stat-num tokens */
        .stat-strip {
            background: rgba(29,179,168,0.07);
            border: 1px solid rgba(29,179,168,0.18);
            border-radius: var(--radius-panel);
            padding: 38px;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
        }
        .stat-num {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 44px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-red), var(--brand-teal));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .stat-label { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-muted); margin-top: 6px; }

        /* Feature section label */
        .features-intro { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .features-intro h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem); letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--ink); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar.ejs', { page: 'home' }) %>

    <div class="page-hero text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-emoji-row">🚸 🚲 🛴 🚗</div>
            <h1 class="display-5" style="color:white;font-family:var(--font-display);letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Road Safety Begins With You</h1>
            <p class="mx-auto" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.82);font-size:17px;max-width:700px;">
                A road safety resource built for youth in Singapore — pedestrians, cyclists, PMD riders
                and future drivers. Learn the rules, know the risks, and help make our roads safer.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-4 mb-2">
                <%- include('partials/searchBar.ejs') %>
            </div>

            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 mt-4 flex-wrap">
                <a href="/guidelines" class="btn-brand">Read Safety Guidelines</a>
                <a href="/causes" class="btn-brand-outline">See the Risks</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-4">

        <%- include('partials/readAloud.ejs') %>

        <div id="readable-content">
        <!-- Stat strip -->
        <div class="stat-strip">
            <div class="row text-center g-4">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="stat-num">147</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Road traffic deaths in Singapore in 2025 — the highest in a decade</div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="stat-num">7,560</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Injury-causing traffic accidents in 2025, up ~7% from 2024</div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="stat-num">76%</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">of Singaporeans polled say impatience is the top reason road users break traffic rules</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="source-note text-center mt-3 mb-0">Source: Singapore Police Force, Annual Road Traffic Situation 2025 &amp; Ministry of Home Affairs (2026)</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Features Section -->
        <div class="mb-5">
            <div class="features-intro">
                <span class="section-label">Explore</span>
                <h2>What You Can Do Here</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card-tile">
                        <div class="icon">📘</div>
                        <h5>Safety Guidelines</h5>
                        <p>Practical, official tips for pedestrians, cyclists, PMD riders and passengers, drawn from SPF and LTA guidance.</p>
                        <a href="/guidelines">Read guidelines &rarr;</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card-tile">
                        <div class="icon">📊</div>
                        <h5>Causes of Accidents</h5>
                        <p>Understand why accidents happen in Singapore — speeding, distraction, PMD misuse and more — backed by real data.</p>
                        <a href="/causes">See the data &rarr;</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card-tile card-tile-urgent">
                        <h5>Emergency Hotlines</h5>
                        <p>Know exactly who to call if you witness or are involved in a road accident — before you ever need it.</p>
                        <a href="/hotlines" style="color:var(--brand-red);">View hotlines &rarr;</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-5">
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card-tile">
                        <div class="icon">✍️</div>
                        <h5>Petitions &amp; Advocacy</h5>
                        <p>See how ordinary Singaporeans have pushed for safer roads — from PMD regulation to tougher penalties for reckless driving.</p>
                        <a href="/petitions">View petitions &rarr;</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card-tile">
                        <div class="icon">📰</div>
                        <h5>News &amp; Media</h5>
                        <p>Stay current on Singapore's latest road safety campaigns, enforcement changes and community initiatives.</p>
                        <a href="/newsNmedia">Read the news &rarr;</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Quote Section -->
        <div class="quote-section text-center text-white p-4 p-md-5 rounded-4 mb-5" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ink) 0%, var(--brand-teal-dark) 100%); position:relative; overflow:hidden;">
            <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%,rgba(29,179,168,0.18) 0%,transparent 55%);pointer-events:none;"></div>
            <blockquote class="mb-2" style="font-size: 20px; font-style: italic; position:relative; z-index:1;">
                "Road safety does not begin at the traffic junction. It begins the moment we step out of our homes —
                in our attitudes, our choices, and how we look out for one another."
            </blockquote>
            <cite style="opacity: 0.7; font-size: 14px; position:relative; z-index:1;">— Singapore Road Safety Month 2026, "Road Safety Begins with You"</cite>
        </div>
        </div><!-- /#readable-content -->

    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>
